     <h2 class="title"><span>Meet SRMB</span></h2>
     <div class = "about-text">
   <p>
   SRMB Srijan Private Limited is an IMS (ISO 9001:2015/ISO 14001: 2015/OHSAS 8001:2007) certified six decades-old Primary Steel Producer (classified by Joint Plant Committee under Ministry of Steel). We manufacture TMT bars, CRS TMT Bars & Structural items with a turnover of more than 1200 crore per annum. The SRMB group has a modern integrated steel plant at Rourkela, Odisha (Bhaskar Steel & Ferro Alloys Private Limited) that manufactures steel semis (billets) from iron ore. SRMB manufactures TMT Bars and structural steel from its captive raw material (billet) in the two state-of-the-art finished steel production units in Durgapur (West Bengal). Our manufacturing units are equipped with all kinds of modern infrastructure, including digital universal testing machine and spectrometer, for quality control and testing purposes.
   SRMB TMT Bars are manufactured in technical collaboration with CRM, Belgium's TEMPCORE Cooling Technology and are the only steel manufacturer in India that has Tempcore License for up to Fe 550 grade and BIS License for up to Fe 600 grade for all available dia. including ductile (D) & S grades. Recently,  the company has also introduced its SR (seismic-resistant) variety of TMT bars, a product suitable for use in earthquake-prone zones. This is the result of SRMB’s motto of “ Leadership through Innovation” innovation by way of adoption of new technologies and in-house research and development.
