                        <h2 class="title"><span class = "headng">Brief History Of The Group</span></h2>  
                        <div class="bottom-line"></div>
                        <div class="title-desc">
 <p><span class = "year">1999 .</span>The company was originally promoted as The Steel Rolling Mills of Bengal Limited.</p>
<p><span class = "year">1999 .</span> Steel Authority of India Ltd. appointed The Steel Rolling Mills of Bengal Limited as their conversion agent.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2000 .</span>Installed First TMT plant in Private sector in India in tie-up with HSE GMBH, Germany.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2001 .</span>The name of the company changed to SRMB Udyog Limited.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2001 .</span>Group started a new Company in the name of SRMB Srijan Private Limited.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2003 .</span>First FE 500+ grade TMT bar launched in the retail sector with marked ‘X’ ribs designed by ‘SRMB’.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2005 .</span> Manufacturing unit installed at Durgapur.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2007 .</span> SRMB Srijan Private Limited become Public Limited Company.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2008 .</span>Added manufacturing unit at Durgapur with capacity by 1.10 Lacs MTPA to produce TMT bars.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2008 .</span>SRMB Srijan Private amalgamated with SRMB Srijan Limited.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2008 .</span>Steel Authority of India Ltd. has appointed SRMB Srijan Ltd. – Durgapur unit as their conversion agent.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2008 .</span>First to establish nationwide retail showroom for TMT Bars with testing Facilities.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2009 .</span>Expansion project with backward integration undertaken at Bankura, WB.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2009 .</span>Launched SRMB SR Earthquake proof TMT bars in India.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2010 .</span>Strategic investment in shares of Bhaskar Steel &amp; Ferro Alloy Ltd Having its plant located at Rourkela, Orissa, by SRMB group &amp; it’s nominees for an assured long term quality supplies of billets as a steptowards backward integration. The said Company is manufacturing sponge iron, billets and power for captive consumption.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2011 .</span>Modernisation and Upgration of Unit 1 at Durgapur.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2012 .</span>Launched construction chemical division.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2013 .</span>Launched GRILL products with the brand name of SRMB REAL EDGE.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2014 .</span>Undertook the hot charging billet plant as backward integration at the existing plant at Durgapur.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2015 .</span>Installed the Facilities for the erection of Angle; channel, flat etc as product diversification.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2016 .</span>SRMB Srijan Limited become a Private Limited Company.</p>
<p><span class = "year">2017 .</span>Implemented Hot Billet Project at Durgapur.</p></div>         </div>
